  ./docs/FUNCTIONAL_SPEC.md:57:The harness uses a single coordinates filter `-Pcoordinates=` accepting `all`, `group:artifact`, `group:artifact:version`, or shard `k/n`. It also exposes authoring helpers (`generateMetadata`, `splitTestOnlyMetadata`, `fixTestNativeImageRun`, `addTestedVersion`, `fetchExistingLibrariesWithNewerVersions`), reporting tasks (`jacocoTestReport`, `generateDynamicAccessCoverageReport`, `generateLibraryStats`, `analyzeExternalLibraryDynamicAccess`), and the `package` release task. The full task reference lives in [DEVELOPING.md](DEVELOPING.md).
